{"tid":2259978,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"總統秘密權力迹近獨裁","createTime":"2020-10-27T08:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T08:38:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2dff4a5b6b8ad373f1c01619878966400317bb93","tid":2259978,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:28:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/IMACF63TONBXLBMMCHZXB5KD3M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FIMACF63TONBXLBMMCHZXB5KD3M%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETfPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=e6699b80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FIMACF63TONBXLBMMCHZXB5KD3M%2F&h=b80fa3aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/IMACF63TONBXLBMMCHZXB5KD3M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n總統秘密權力迹近獨裁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/v0xHg77IYKR8GEsKQY6ow41gjy0=/3248x996/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BWFCSX4JXBAPNGMFGD42VHWSQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fv0xHg77IYKR8GEsKQY6ow41gjy0%3D%2F3248x996%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBWFCSX4JXBAPNGMFGD42VHWSQA.jpg&h=2acc0b78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■外界擔心特朗普若大選失利又不認輸，他的狂熱支持者或會生事。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普今年3月、4月和7日都曾公開談到總統權力，他是有「絕對」權力「有權做任何想做的事」，而大眾甚至是對總統有這樣權力的事毫無頭緒。這些發言都被傳媒一一駁斥。但事實是美國總統確有「迹近獨裁」的「秘密權力」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：布殊 戈爾為選票對簿公堂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簽名即可執行<br />\n<br />\n特朗普的言論觸發紐約大學法學院布倫南法律中心（Brennan Center for Justice）進行審視，。。。。。。。。。。。，而且絕大部份都是總統簽名就可執行。<br />\n<br />\n總統的「非常權力」亦不公開，分析認為多半包括可下令進行新聞審查、拘捕美國境內「外來敵人」、實行戒嚴、毋須獲法庭命令而進行搜查、暫緩人身保護權等權力。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：軍方高層誓保政治中立<br />\n<br />\n一些法律學者認為總統緊急行動文件並不合憲，。。。。。。。。。。。，「無論掌政的人是誰，美國人民都有權知道總統掌有的特別權力」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《獨立報》"},{"pid":"6dbac164073e3303656aaf33